.container
    .row
        .col-lg-10.mx-lg-auto
            h1.lead.mt-5
                | I write about technology, culture, and things I come across as interesting both at work and outside of work.
            ul.list-unstyled.mt-5
                each blog in blogs
                    a.text-reset.text-decoration-none(
                        href="/blog/" + blog.id + "/"
                    )
                        li.media.mb-1
                            img.mr-4(
                                src="/blogs/" + blog.id + "/images/thumbnail.png"
                                width="64"
                                height="64"
                                alt=blog.title + ' thumbnail'
                            )
                            .media-body
                                h5.mt-0.mb-1.font-weight-normal=blog.title
                                p=blog.summary